[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ふう……とりあえず神聖国の使者ってことで\nベスティラの王様と王妃様に謁見はできそうだね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00901",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "なんかさっき街で聞いたけど、ここの王様は\n気さくだから誰でも会ってくれるみたいだよ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_00902",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ええっ、ありがたい限り……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00903",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "そんな気のいい王様なら、事情を話したら\n「九偉人図」も気前良く譲ってくれたりして",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00904",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ベスティラ王",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "よくぞ参った！\n遠路遥々ご苦労だったな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_707_036_00905",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "でっ……でっか……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_00906",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "い、いかにも屈強な戦士ってカンジ……\nなるほど、これは誰とでも会えるはずですわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00907",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "悪い人に襲われても、返り討ちにしちゃいそうだね……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00908",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ベスティラ王",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "して、神聖国の使者よ！\n我がベスティラに何用だ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_707_036_00909",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "あ、はい！　王様がかつてブラオールの商会から買った\n「九偉人図」という絵を……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00910",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ベスティラ王",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ああ、あの絵か。\nあれはいいものだ。作者の魂、情念が籠っている",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_707_036_00911",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "その、お気に入りの絵を、恐縮ですが\nお譲りいただけないものかと……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00912",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ベスティラ王妃",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "あれは、王様がとーっても気に入ってるんだよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_708_036_00913",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ベスティラ王妃",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "交渉できるようなものじゃないと思うけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_708_036_00914",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "いやぁ、厚かましいのは百も承知ですが。\n人の業といいますか、それでも欲しくてですね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00915",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "いくらでしたら\nお譲りいただけるでしょうか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00916",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ベスティラ王",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "金はいらん。代わりに、お前らの生き様を見せろ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_707_036_00917",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "生き様……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00918",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ベスティラ王",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "この世で最も大切なものは、金でも、命でもない。\n生き様だ。どう生き、どう死ぬか……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_707_036_00919",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ベスティラ王",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "九偉人図、あれには描き手の生き様が込められている。\nあれを欲するのなら、それ相応の生き様を見せてみろ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_707_036_00920",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "これは……獣人限定、ベスティラ武道会の告知？\n全員一斉参加、最後まで残った者が勝利……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00921",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "優勝者にはベスティラ王が可能な範囲で\n願いを１つ叶えてくれる……これに参加しろと？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_003_036_00922",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ベスティラ王",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "そうだ。これに勝ち残り、「九偉人図」を望むがいい。\n見たところお前も腕に覚えがあるのだろう？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_707_036_00923",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ベスティラ王",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "欲しいものがあるのならば、\nお前の生き様で、掴み取ってみせるがいい！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_707_036_00924",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ベスティラ王妃",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ほーんと、この人ったら戦うの大好きだよねー。\n戦うより楽しいこと、いっぱいあるのにねー？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_708_036_00925",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ベスティラ王妃",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "たとえば……そこの子猫ちゃん。お名前は？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_708_036_00926",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "い、イザナと申します",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_00927",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ベスティラ王妃",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "へえ、イザナちゃんっていうんだ。\nうわぁめちゃくちゃかわいー、ちょっと耳触らせてー？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_708_036_00928",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "え、いや、耳は……その、アタシの生まれた村の掟で、\n心に決めた人にしか触らせてはいけないんです！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_00929",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "ベスティラ王妃",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "やだ、想い人がいるのー？\nそう言われると余計欲しくなっちゃうなあ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_708_036_00930",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "ベスティラ王",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "はっはっは！\nかようにわがままなところもかわいい奴よ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_707_036_00931",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ベスティラ王",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "しかし、話は武道会が終わってからにしようではないか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_707_036_00932",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "ベスティラ王妃",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "はいはい。ふふ、イザナちゃん。また後でね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_708_036_00933",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "イザナちゃん……私いつも耳触っちゃってたけど……\nど、どうしよう、知らなかった！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00934",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "えへ。嘘だよー、うそうそ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_00935",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]